T1  - Taxes, unequal access, public debt and corporate financial policy in the United Kingdom
AU  - Fung, W.K.F
AU  - Theobald, M.F
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 11
IS  - 1
SP  - 65
EP  - 78
